NUMBER 198
NAME Rats' den
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
INDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Years of neglect have allowed the rats to expand this hole into a large den. Bits of fur and rodent droppings matted together on the floor form a soft, but disgusting rug.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 2022
ITEM 0 427
ITEM 1 362
ITEM 2 422
IFVERB FLIP 2
	IFVAR ORG = 40
		ECHO PLAYER You activate the security device.
		ECHO OTHERS %N activates the contraption.
		GMMSG %N needs NSHADES.SCR compiled at this time.
		SPELL 406 100
		SPELL 405 100
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ORG ! 40
		ADD FLAG1 1
		IFVAR FLAG1 < 2
			ECHO PLAYER You know you shouldn't mess with things you do not understand.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR FLAG1 >= 2
			ECHO OTHERS %N mishandles the device!
			DAMAGE ELECTRIC 75 %N gets the shock of %h life!
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
PUT 1 550 VAL2=409
IFSAY open
	IFVAR intnum55 = 4
		NEWITEM 9 72 VAL2=197
    GMMSG %N needs NSHADES.SCR compiled at this time.
		ECHO ALL An opening shimmers into view.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB go 9
	ECHO OTHERS The opening closes behind %n.
	MOVE 197
	REMOVEITEM 9
ENDIF
IFSAY close
	IFVAR intnum55 = 4
		IFITEM 9
			REMOVEITEM 9
			ECHO ALL The opening closes.
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB GO 0
	IFVAR ORG = 40
		ECHO PLAYER You slip into an unseen crevice.
		ECHO OTHERS %N goes out.
		MOVE 197
		AFFECT 197
		ECHO OTHERS The hole opens for a moment and %n comes in.
		AFFECT 2022
		CLEARVERB
	ENDIF
ENDIF
