NUMBER 225
NAME Test Tunnels, Entrance
FIXED_LIGHT
INDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A number of guards, wearing the livery of the Adventurers' Guild, are posted
here, at the entrance to the Test Tunnels. They stand at the ready, watching
for any signs of monsters trying to escape from the arch that leads to the
Test Tunnels. On the east wall, behind a worn, oaken desk sits a scribe who
records the names of all who enter the Tunnels. Above the archway is a bronze
plaque with some writing upon its polished surface. The muffled sounds of
combat can be heard emanating through the archway. A stairway leads back
up to the Adventurers' Guild Training area.
*DESCRIPTION_END
