*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
You recognize several people in this portrait from around town, including a weaver-pirate, a large red cat, a kid in a cowboy hat, a silver woman with silver hair, a maratasen, an ex-murg, a dark man with dreadlocks, a mute bard, something that may or may not be a dead cat, and several others as well. A small label beneath reads, "The Last Resort"
*DESCRIPTION_END
