         ECHO OTHERS The maitre d' bows to %N and says, "Good evening, sir."
      ENDIF
      IFVAR GEN = 1
         ECHO PLAYER Jean-Tom, the maitre d', bows to you and says, "Good evening madam, we have many tables available tonight, so you may find a seat at your leisure."
         ECHO OTHERS The maitre d' bows to %N and says, "Good evening, madam."
      ENDIF
      IFVAR GEN = 2
         ECHO PLAYER The maitre d' frowns once at you, then proceeds to pointedly ignore you.
         ECHO OTHERS The maitre d' frowns at %N.
      ENDIF
