   IFVAR DISGUISED = 1
      ECHO PLAYER The maitre d' frowns at you and snaps his fingers. Two burly men in tuxedoes grab you by the shoulders and toss you out onto the street.
      ECHO OTHERS %N tries to enter, but the maitre d' quickly summons two large men to toss %h back out. Apparently they dislike deceit here.
      ECHO PLAYER On the way out, he whispers to you, "Sorry, but we don't tolerate deceit in the Cafe de la Paix."
      EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
      ECHO PLAYER [Round: 10 seconds]
      POSITION LAY
      MOVE 3524
   ENDIF
ENDIF
