NUMBER 3633
NAME Cafe, Kitchen
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The kitchen is a bustle of activity. People in white aprons move this way and that, stoking the oven, checking pots of water on the stove, adding spices here and there, and many other things as well. Waiters come in, take completed dishes, and leave again though the swinging doors.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
EXIT O 3630
ITEM 0 438
IFPREVERB SNIFF -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO OTHERS %N sniffs.
  ECHO PLAYER The plethora of scents which reaches your nose is astounding.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SEARCH -1
  CLEARVERB
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 2
  ECHO PLAYER You notice a rat scurry under a table.
  ECHO PLAYER [Round: 2 seconds]
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GET 0
  CLEARVERB
  RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
  EQUAL ITEMVAL5 DUMMY1
  MOD ITEMVAL5 100
  EQUAL ITEMVAL3 SKILL4
  MULT ITEMVAL3 5
  IFVAR ITEMVAL3 > ITEMVAL5
    ECHO PLAYER You pounce on %a, catching it before it can scurry away!
    ECHO OTHERS %N pounces on %a, catching it before it can scurry away!
    NEWITEM -1 439  ADJ1=405  VAL2=8
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You try to grab %a, but it scurries away.
    ECHO OTHERS %N tries to grab %a, but it scurries away.
  ENDIF
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
  ECHO PLAYER [Round: 5 seconds]
ENDIF
