NUMBER 3800
NAME Hadan Kentarus Avenue
FIXED_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The silver and gold specks in the river-rock stones forming the walkway sparkle
like faerie dust. Sprigs of holly have been tacked to the doorframe of a wooden
building, its window shutters and decorative wood trim painted forest green.
Several shallow clay bowls have been placed on either side of the entryway,
along with some colorful handmade mats.
*DESCRIPTION_END
